    "body": "Drivers that are CUDA 12.1+ compatible provide the ability to programmatically control GPU core dumps, see https://docs.nvidia.com/cuda/cuda-driver-api/group__CUDA__COREDUMP.html#group__CUDA__COREDUMP.  This can remove the limitations encountered with #9238 where we cannot always programmatically control the environment variables of an executor process.\r\n\r\nWe should add native bindings to use these APIs and the ability to safely detect when they are available.",
